{"tid":1807053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣都冇割港獨，連登仔就爭住出嚟叫人唔好嗌","createTime":"2020-01-01T15:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T16:15:37.000Z","uid":79382,"like":147,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"5c17c5af99aa2dc8c58cf5cd478eb1fbfb26c0ad","tid":1807053,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:32:50.000Z","msg":"近幾次集會都越來越多人叫<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「香港獨立，唯一出路」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔少上咗年紀嘅Uncle、Auntie都有跟，<br />\n今日手足直頭上台拎埋mic嗌，<br />\n之後民陣都識講「尊重光譜唔同嘅聲音」<br />\n<br />\n即刻諗起早兩日連登勁多人開post：<br />\n「港獨唔好講出嚟」<br />\n「唔好嗌港獨，陷害民陣」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d385a811f2d3b1b94284372afd84f847271d167","tid":1807053,"uid":79382,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:36:11.000Z","msg":"一齊講：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港獨立</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7e909d7f36b36becc57d67c25053b32235c675a7","tid":1807053,"uid":124859,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:37:36.000Z","msg":"香港獨立！"},{"pid":"32c14c45d3106c18415794bb538b2e2a4ada2c6f","tid":1807053,"uid":59297,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:38:30.000Z","msg":"港獨思潮<br />\n黃色經濟圈<br />\n組織工會<br />\n<br />\n呢三者將會係我地2020嘅抗爭目標，三者缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先要思想武裝，認清只有獨立一途，香港已經冇險可守，香港人係一個民族，完全異於所謂中國人，應該建立一個屬於自己嘅國家。<br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈同工會就係行動實踐，建立返香港民族嘅經濟實力，從各行各業建立力量，再加強理念宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n去到獨立嘅最後一步，就係等待歷史機會，當中共最脆弱嘅時候，全球反共嘅時候，引用國際法嘅住民自決原則，透過公投宣布獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca6a57613431cc2abe6d2d849080d18564539b1","tid":1807053,"uid":71341,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:39:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf06683815748102d047afebd2709e697432a663","tid":1807053,"uid":6347,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:39:34.000Z","msg":"支持你搞港獨集會"},{"pid":"08ab6d0954847534751e567162331a8c0b34813d","tid":1807053,"uid":79382,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7e909d7f36b36becc57d67c25053b32235c675a7","tid":1807053,"uid":124859,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:37:36.000Z","msg":"香港獨立！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:39:40.000Z","msg":"唯一出路！"},{"pid":"dce838d6f58aabf3d3a1d74c3306145341af100b","tid":1807053,"uid":259812,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:40:09.000Z","msg":"民陣好似淨係講句台下口號不代表民陣立場，係連登仔爭住割咋嘛"},{"pid":"ace5c45c53cf4e4ceea857cbbbc55a13e1e59286","tid":1807053,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32c14c45d3106c18415794bb538b2e2a4ada2c6f","tid":1807053,"uid":59297,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:38:30.000Z","msg":"港獨思潮<br />\n黃色經濟圈<br />\n組織工會<br />\n<br />\n呢三者將會係我地2020嘅抗爭目標，三者缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先要思想武裝，認清只有獨立一途，香港已經冇險可守，香港人係一個民族，完全異於所謂中國人，應該建立一個屬於自己嘅國家。<br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈同工會就係行動實踐，建立返香港民族嘅經濟實力，從各行各業建立力量，再加強理念宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n去到獨立嘅最後一步，就係等待歷史機會，當中共最脆弱嘅時候，全球反共嘅時候，引用國際法嘅住民自決原則，透過公投宣布獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:40:37.000Z","msg":"非常認同<br />\n而且香港要向國際社會輸出革命，建立反華包圍網"},{"pid":"5e38e90d09d7519878957c45aa7f6177f46f1240","tid":1807053,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:40:49.000Z","msg":"尊重 不等於 不提出反對意見"},{"pid":"0a0491d0821d4484f884a28fc9dee57da7dd2c39","tid":1807053,"uid":79382,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5e38e90d09d7519878957c45aa7f6177f46f1240","tid":1807053,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:40:49.000Z","msg":"尊重 不等於 不提出反對意見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:42:51.000Z","msg":"正如我唔認同林奠下台<br />\n但人哋嗌到，我唔跟就得<br />\n想嗌咩就嗌咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1773b63a7c40b3ab955a4100181fdb43d02cd20","tid":1807053,"uid":71092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:42:57.000Z","msg":"今日第一次嗌 開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de55d67d753f32a636872dd59688dc8b7a3bc18","tid":1807053,"uid":332804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:44:40.000Z","msg":"反對不等於割，我會叫人唔好嗌，但你嗌係你嘅自由，唔會阻止你。"},{"pid":"df7dd1f42d454a9846492fb5d211e367f67872cf","tid":1807053,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ace5c45c53cf4e4ceea857cbbbc55a13e1e59286","tid":1807053,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32c14c45d3106c18415794bb538b2e2a4ada2c6f","tid":1807053,"uid":59297,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:38:30.000Z","msg":"港獨思潮<br />\n黃色經濟圈<br />\n組織工會<br />\n<br />\n呢三者將會係我地2020嘅抗爭目標，三者缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先要思想武裝，認清只有獨立一途，香港已經冇險可守，香港人係一個民族，完全異於所謂中國人，應該建立一個屬於自己嘅國家。<br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈同工會就係行動實踐，建立返香港民族嘅經濟實力，從各行各業建立力量，再加強理念宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n去到獨立嘅最後一步，就係等待歷史機會，當中共最脆弱嘅時候，全球反共嘅時候，引用國際法嘅住民自決原則，透過公投宣布獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:40:37.000Z","msg":"非常認同<br />\n而且香港要向國際社會輸出革命，建立反華包圍網"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"依家我地已經有國際關注，接下來就係睇我地表演點樣對抗中國經濟殖民，靠黃色經濟圈同公會去生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上全球好多國家都俾中國經濟殖民緊，所以因為錢要睇中共面色，只要我地香港做到先驅，竟然可以唔奶共都有出路，全球就會跟住我地，之後支爆就不遠了，光復香港都不遠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de79f4e1dc42ed8d73ef56fe0069754350798bf","tid":1807053,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:45:57.000Z","msg":"香港獨立"},{"pid":"df90a227584e4b589ada265eb2b0eac9e0cd5029","tid":1807053,"uid":79382,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7ca6a57613431cc2abe6d2d849080d18564539b1","tid":1807053,"uid":71341,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"7e909d7f36b36becc57d67c25053b32235c675a7","tid":1807053,"uid":124859,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:37:36.000Z","msg":"香港獨立！"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:39:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:46:51.000Z","msg":"咁五大訴求同光復香港都唔使<br />\n數落去應該只可以嗌香港人加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb45f4805808d52454d753b043b341e6782b3880","tid":1807053,"uid":83914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:46:58.000Z","msg":"番到屋企早D沖涼...聽日重要番工..休息一段時間<br />\n<br />\n谷一日休六日...成功近在眼前"},{"pid":"2e81b34c5382cec64f055ff1d8c5d4b85e1f3377","tid":1807053,"uid":31151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:47:31.000Z","msg":"沒有兩國 那有兩制"},{"pid":"75bad9714b84125d885358be2cf718b07803b2e8","tid":1807053,"uid":210140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c17c5af99aa2dc8