e":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:49:24.000Z","msg":"今日叫左好多次香港獨立 唯一出路 大家都有跟住叫 雖然唔及其他口號次數多 但係係第一步黎 好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:19:37.000Z","msg":"逐漸成為主流民意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae49d074b8d0f0fc0596210d51f7f8f0112239ff","tid":1807053,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:20:58.000Z","msg":"言論自由上係隨便大家嗌<br />\n策略上認唔認同係第二件事<br />\n我支持港獨 但唔支持呢一刻明搞<br />\n正如啲外國記者幫口問小粉紅時<br />\n都會針住話我地無要求分裂國家而收佢地皮<br />\n雙真普選其實kind of 帶緊去自決獨立嘅方向<br />\n只係呢個講法仲有基本法呢塊遮醜布<br />\n令政府支共同小粉紅無得好直接咁反對<br />\n<br />\nAnyway其實都唔明拗嚟做乜<br />\n鍾意講咪講 唔講都可以尊重其他人<br />\n同路人越拉越少 無分化空間啦<br />\n仲自己幫支那做政治審查係咪傻㗎<br />\n個point係點做 唔係去拗講唔講<br />\n亦唔好人地唔撐就一句港豬隊埋去<br />\n會無咗好多有意義嘅討論空間"},{"pid":"4d59eaa1fe8ab7916938b6a89dea9835804035e6","tid":1807053,"uid":32675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ca6a57613431cc2abe6d2d849080d18564539b1","tid":1807053,"uid":71341,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"7e909d7f36b36becc57d67c25053b32235c675a7","tid":1807053,"uid":124859,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:37:36.000Z","msg":"香港獨立！"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:39:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:21:57.000Z","msg":"藍屍白痴,死無全屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打得嬴,講得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44801e049282d5d725073eeffe411e1e0adf0455","tid":1807053,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:22:54.000Z","msg":"香港獨立！"},{"pid":"86a1170236a2336b0138bf99c104cbeec72c8f63","tid":1807053,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e909d7f36b36becc57d67c25053b32235c675a